import random
import time
from selenium import webdriver
from selenium.webdriver.common.by import By
from selenium.webdriver.common.keys import Keys
from selenium.webdriver.support.ui import WebDriverWait
from selenium.webdriver.support import expected_conditions as EC

driver = webdriver.Chrome()
driver.get("http://192.168.1.1")

username_input = WebDriverWait(driver, 10).until(
    EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, "txt_Username"))
)
password_input = WebDriverWait(driver, 10).until(
    EC.presence_of_element_located((By.ID, "txt_Password"))
)

username_input.send_keys("admin")
password_input.send_keys("admin")
time.sleep(2)
password_input.send_keys(Keys.RETURN)

driver.switch_to.frame("menufrm")
wait = WebDriverWait(driver, 10)
basic_button = wait.until(EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.XPATH, "//a[contains(text(), 'Настройки')]")))
basic_button.click()
driver.switch_to.default_content()
driver.switch_to.frame("contentfrm")

mtu_input = wait.until(EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.NAME , "mtuSize")))
mtu_value = random.randint(1480, 1490)
mtu_input.clear()
mtu_input.send_keys(mtu_value)

mtu_button = wait.until(EC.element_to_be_clickable((By.NAME , "btnApply")))
mtu_button.click()

time.sleep(3)
driver.quit()
